# 💰 Gym Log Tracker — Monetization & Feature Strategy

## The Math

| Metric | Value |
|---|---|
| **Price** | $2.99 one-time |
| **Revenue Goal** | $2,000 |
| **App Store Cut** | ~30% (Apple/Google) |
| **Net per Sale** | ~$2.09 |
| **Sales Needed** | **~957 sales** |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> After the 30% store commission, you need **~957 paid downloads** to net $2,000. This is very achievable for a well-positioned fitness app — the gym fitness app market is valued at **$12+ billion in 2025** and growing 26% yearly.

