## Summary

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Start with Features #1 (Programs) and #2 (PR Tracking).** These two alone can justify the $2.99 price and drive the majority of your sales. The "no subscription" angle combined with built-in programs is a **proven winning formula** in the fitness app market.

The combination of:
- ✅ Pre-built programs (main purchase driver)
- ✅ PR celebrations (emotional hook)  
- ✅ Gamification/streaks (retention → reviews → organic growth)
- ✅ "No subscription" positioning (competitive advantage)

...gives you a realistic path to **957+ sales** within the first 3-6 months.
